Brooke McCarter https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brooke_McCarter 0 Brooke McCarter (April 22, 1963 – December 22, 2015) was an American actor, producer, director, composer and musician. He is known for the role of Paul in the 1987 vampire horror comedy The Lost Boys.
